  "title": "Retail Sales Assistant",
  "description": "<p><strong>Industry:</strong> Mobile Accessories<br /><strong>Working Days:</strong> <strong>5.5 days a week</strong><br /><strong>Working Hours:</strong> <strong>11:00 AM – 9:00 PM Monday - Friday, 11:00 AM - 3:00 PM Saturday</strong><br /><strong>Location:</strong> United Square<br /><strong>Employment Type:</strong> Full-time</p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><p>Attend to walk-in customers and provide friendly customer service</p></li><li><p>Promote and sell mobile accessories such as phone cases, screen protectors, chargers, cables, and earphones</p></li><li><p>Recommend suitable products based on customers’ needs</p></li><li><p>Handle cashiering and daily shop operations</p></li><li><p>Maintain shop cleanliness and proper product display</p></li><li><p>Assist with stock checking and replenishment</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><p>Friendly and positive attitude</p></li><li><p>Retail or mobile accessories experience is an advantage</p></li><li><p>Able to work weekends and public holidays</p></li></ul><p><strong>Salary </strong></p><ul><li><p>Basic Salary + Sales Commission</p></li></ul>",
